# Workflow Rules
## Before writing any code
1. State the single task in one sentence
2. Is this CORE (without it the app breaks) or FEATURE (nice to have)?
3. CORE → do now. FEATURE → add to TASKS.md, do later.
## Build order (never skip steps)
1. Data model → 2. Core logic → 3. Terminal test → 4. API → 5. UI → 6. Features
## Commit format
- feat(scope): description
- fix(scope): description  
- refactor(scope): description
- docs: description
- chore: description
## Commit timing: after every working unit, not end of day
## After every task: update STATUS.md (NOW/NEXT/BLOCKED)
